value: Binary protein-protein interactions (PPIs) for Drosophila melanogaster, containing 8723 PPIs among 2939 proteins. The iteractions were identified using a yeast two-hybrid (Y2H) analysis.

['Tang, HW., Spirohn, K., Hu, Y. et al. Next-generation large-scale binary protein interaction network for Drosophila melanogaster. Nat Commun 14, 2162 (2023), https://doi.org/10.1038/s41467-023-37876-0']
